headline: Netflix's record streak, Instacart surges, Uber robotaxi deal
summary: Yahoo Finance Julie Hyman tracks major market (^GSPC, ^IXIC, ^DJI) moves and trending stocks. Netflix (NFLX) shares rose after logging 11 straight days of gains following earnings. Instacart (CART) — which operates as Maplebear, Inc. — projects accelerating order growth and a better-than-expected second quarter EBITDA outlook, while Uber (UBER) plans to roll out autonomous vehicles in Europe in 2026 through a new deal with Beijing’s Momenta Technology. Stay up to date on the latest market action, minute-by-minute, with Yahoo Finance's Market Minute.
